Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:06.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是某個冬日的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼偏偏是這個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:20.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:43.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:46.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用謝 我也要去同個地方考試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:51.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你很害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後 直到考場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:18.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火都沒有放開我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 我的初戀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:26.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡衣好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:27.70,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:32.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在遇到她之前 我一直以為自己只是討厭男生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,或是單純對戀愛沒有興趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:44.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我察覺到了這份心情的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:47.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是花火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
