Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.50,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)\an8}一番大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.04,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:16.76,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな単純なことが今は一番出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.50,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}もしも運命があるのならば　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.20,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「あなたは運命の人」なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:26.98,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな言葉今を壊しそうで言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.62,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近くに居ても遠く感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.18,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}行ったり来たりしてるこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:35.24,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}諦める　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.32,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}終わらない花占い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.86,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}宝箱の鍵失ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.38,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}キラキラした想いて抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:50.22,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}ほのかに色付いた欠片をため息に隠す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.48,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}目が合ったなら逸らさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.12,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}秘められたこの嘘を見抜いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.56,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}限界がもう分からないの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.20,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}だから今は何も言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.72,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}苦しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.04,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}怖いほどあなたが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.08,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.50,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.04,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最想要去珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:16.76,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如此簡單的事情現在卻最無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.50,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若是真的存在命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.20,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「你就是我的命定之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:26.98,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}無法說出口 懼怕這些話語將會毀掉現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.62,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近在咫尺卻彷若遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.18,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}反覆無常的這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:35.24,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}放棄 還是堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.32,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}永無止境的花瓣占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.86,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若然丟失了寶箱的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:42.38,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}抱緊最後一絲希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:50.22,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}將逐漸泛紅的碎片藏進一聲聲嘆息中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.48,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如果看著我 請不要移開目光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.12,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}讓你看透我所隱藏的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.56,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}我不知自己能堅持到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.20,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}所以現在請你沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.72,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}愛的如此痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:19.04,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}愛的如此恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------op -----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:26.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後啊 說是想要找我戀愛諮詢才去了家庭餐廳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:28.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻一直談對方的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼兩邊都想要都不想分手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.47,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼做的話誰都留不住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火真是純情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後會變成孤身一人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火睏了嗎 要睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊床有點小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟 糟糕 要被她聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:10.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好聞的洗髮水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:14.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我身上也帶著同樣的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:18.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡的人是什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:35.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小繪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:05.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其實你並不是很喜歡粟屋對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.85,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要假裝喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一次賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.87,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我從花火身上感受到的違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我想多了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就徹底放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我一直注視著花火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:48.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小繪…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我有 喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個人不會喜歡上我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才和麥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:12.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無語了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.96,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,選我也可以的吧
