Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:29.75,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1100)\fn@方正兰亭宋_GBK\frz270\b0\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\fs82.5\pos(513,582)}無論是幸福還是不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:29.75,Kuzu_text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1100)\fn@方正兰亭宋_GBK\frz270\b0\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\fs82.5\pos(633,471)} 我都想要抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:42.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花火 起床了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我去買點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:48.21,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,從你朋友回去之後你就一直呆呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被沒有興趣的人告白示好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比這更噁心的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.40,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我說了這麼噁心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.79,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.38,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人的好感…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是這麼的沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是難得的假日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,無視我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你非要選小麥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:50.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是小麥也沒什麼關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:54.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搶走他啊 我就只有小麥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小麥你不也是一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:15.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦喜歡上 就覺得非那個人莫屬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄任何一方都覺得可惜所以無法決定什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣做的話誰都留不住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後會變成孤單一人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己還不是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只會一味的逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 還未明白這是戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 大家都好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一年級 天真無邪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 芽衣 欲求不滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.50,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.35,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.71,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是中學的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:29.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真工口 特別是早川前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然纖細卻是巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著男孩子氣卻有著說不出的工口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:33.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂你沒興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,纖細卻是巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛吞吞吐吐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:53.55,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩纖細若折 胸卻很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.53,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只記得那晶瑩剔透的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩是容易感到寂寞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.44,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,並非尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.31,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩的身體有些冰涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:25.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人感覺不到現實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:29.91,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,卻只把熱情投向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:33.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:56.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 居然一個人就興奮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我按了門鈴的 門也沒鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我那個什麼在睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,空調不都開到最猛嗎 這房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 真不湊巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 怎麼感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.28,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 豎起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一副很感興趣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:03.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.32,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 高中？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.39,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:23.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很搖滾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搖滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,粟屋很會學習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,考試加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊怎麼了別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:40.06,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡那個家教的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:49.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,結果沒有被任何人知道呢 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:50.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真快樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:53.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:59.24,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在思春期 讓你和我交往真是對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為秘密拯救了心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:09.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本想要把它當作逢場作戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.15,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,事實上 卻是那麼的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果…果然還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.20,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:23.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對會 會忍不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.29,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:25.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…別忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是沒有成長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.62,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,思春期的玩具呢 我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:47.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊痛 快要折斷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.34,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不懂 第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 這樣 試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.86,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.23,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺 總感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:36.22,kuzu_logo,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b0\c&HE685F7&\fs67.5\pos(972,639)\blur22.5\t(0,600,\blur0)}「真可愛呀」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是何等簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:46.33,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此輕易就能觸碰到麥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.88,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為害怕而沒有去接觸小繪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:58.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.12,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 和麥在一起就很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.69,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:14.94,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:21.56,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大概是經常卿卿我我身體都變得很熟練了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有語病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.89,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得像做過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:31.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂為什麼不從被窩裡出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:33.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,超級賢者模式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.27,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說是因為把我衣服弄髒了在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.65,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥 我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:56.51,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想喜歡上麥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.90,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服 洗好了還你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那衣服我蠻喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.07,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.18,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好洗掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:34.09,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,洗掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒洗掉的話後果很嚴重的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,情人旅館什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:42.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然想去些不同的地方 我帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:58.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚…晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和男人在一起 在這種時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且感覺 不是很年輕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.49,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.64,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:10.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我工作的學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.42,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.11,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.63,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦快去找位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.13,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是個超級姐控的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.82,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦快點走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:39.14,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請保密 彼此都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時間和男人在一起 我也是一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.81,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本來我就覺得很可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.76,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.72,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:20.16,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個家庭餐廳裡和茜姐一起的男人 我認識
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:20.92,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.84,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得他已經忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:28.01,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概他和我一樣是茜姐家教的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.97,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一起選參考書的時候遇見過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 什麼然後 只是原來的學生罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.03,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是深夜被叫出去談一些事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛是盲目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是單純的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.80,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:56.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為何不能擁有相同的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.36,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:08.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過稍微相互挨著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有著相同心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:15.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,麥還是喜歡那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.04,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.45,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.43,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.41,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.08,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像這個天空一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如此舒暢痛快的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.60,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡哥哥會遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.68,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比我更合適的人之類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:38.05,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也許在找著放棄的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.17,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.52,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.22,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沸騰起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.59,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:49.73,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是嫌惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.93,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天一起的那個人是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.58,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:18.61,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸嘿嘿 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.57,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是原來的學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.46,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣 什麼也沒有的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.77,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請保密 彼此都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:33.66,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不必特地去煩惱吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.98,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況把那種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:41.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露給那個人的危害是一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.67,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且意識到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥對你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.95,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麥對你的好意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.10,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.30,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:04.74,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,安樂岡同學 放學後繼續 在音樂教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:10.48,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,當時 瀰漫些微香菸的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:15.02,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,茜姐穿著和昨天一樣的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:19.25,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,颯爽地跑開了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kuzu_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}讓我們一起逃離太陽系 在平行線相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如同你我的影子般延伸著 平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}將膽小怯懦歸咎於時代的錯也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}無處可歸的我 找尋著願望的歸所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}只願成為你唇邊溢出的隻言片語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}讓我們一起逃離太陽系 在平行線相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}帶上無法實現的希冀 以及毫無底氣的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}倘若感情全部流失殆盡 便由我開始描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}如今向你我的影子伸出手 平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:33.57,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:48.63,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影のように伸びている　あぁ平行線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.10,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}勇気がないのは時代のせいにしてしまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.47,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}何処にも行けない　願いの居場所を探してた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:09.35,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}君の唇から　こぼれだす　言葉になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:19.82,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}太陽系を抜け出して　平行線で交わろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:30.01,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そんな叶わない望みも　不甲斐ない声も引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:39.58,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}感情全部流しきったら　描き始めてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:50.45,Kuzu_opjp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}私と君の影に今手を伸ばす　あぁ平行線
